      "date": "2011-06-22 05:27:57.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nDo you think it is clearer to revise osc_set_lock_data_with_check() as:\n\nint osc_set_lock_data_with_check(...)\n{\n        void *data = einfo->ei_cbdata;\n        int found = 0;\n\n        LASSERT(...);\n\n        lock_res_and_lock(lock);\n        cfs_spin_lock(&osc_ast_guard);\n        if (lock->l_ast_data == NULL);\n                lock->l_ast_data = data;\n        found = (lock->l_ast_data == data);\n        cfs_spin_unlock(&osc_ast_guard);\n        unlock_res_and_lock(lock);\n\n        return found;\n}",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
